00:30:45,360 --> 00:30:46,360
You eat it.

382
00:30:50,760 --> 00:30:52,680
Choo-choo!

383
00:30:52,760 --> 00:30:55,520
Who likes this flavor?

384
00:30:58,360 --> 00:30:59,880
- Cheers.
- Yeah.

385
00:30:59,960 --> 00:31:00,960
Clink!

386
00:31:01,480 --> 00:31:04,440
Hey, guys, look at this!
Our video on my channel.

387
00:31:04,520 --> 00:31:07,040
The views are insane.

388
00:31:07,120 --> 00:31:08,080
Wow.

389
00:31:08,160 --> 00:31:11,320
Check the comments. "The guitarist
is so handsome, drop his link!"

390
00:31:12,720 --> 00:31:14,120
Hey, you have no idea.

391
00:31:14,200 --> 00:31:16,480
It's the drummer, that's why it blew up.

392
00:31:16,560 --> 00:31:18,480
- No way, no way.
- Guys, stop arguing.

393
00:31:18,560 --> 00:31:20,320
- It's because of me.
- Oh.

394
00:31:20,400 --> 00:31:22,560
- Nonsense.
- Hey, big news! Big news!

395
00:31:22,640 --> 00:31:23,720
What now?

396
00:31:23,800 --> 00:31:26,000
We've just been contacted

397
00:31:26,080 --> 00:31:28,680
- by a record label.
- What?!

398
00:31:29,560 --> 00:31:31,240
- Let me see.
- What does it say?

399
00:31:34,040 --> 00:31:35,760
Wow, is it that easy?

400
00:31:35,840 --> 00:31:38,280
Hey, not that easy.

401
00:31:38,360 --> 00:31:41,360
Do you know how hard
we worked on that song?

402
00:31:42,120 --> 00:31:44,280
We deserve a break at last.

403
00:31:44,360 --> 00:31:45,840
- Yes.
- So,

404
00:31:45,920 --> 00:31:48,560
where should we celebrate?!

405
00:31:49,080 --> 00:31:50,320
Wait, wait.

406
00:31:50,400 --> 00:31:52,040
Chill.

407
00:31:52,120 --> 00:31:54,560
