we have the TGAT exam tomorrow.

408
00:31:54,640 --> 00:31:56,120
Oh, please.

409
00:31:59,080 --> 00:32:01,240
Screw the exam. We're artists now.

410
00:32:01,320 --> 00:32:02,360
Oh.

411
00:32:04,360 --> 00:32:05,560
Hey, anything bugging you?

412
00:32:09,320 --> 00:32:10,440
No.

413
00:32:11,880 --> 00:32:13,120
Nothing.

414
00:32:24,840 --> 00:32:25,920
Snacks.

415
00:32:26,000 --> 00:32:27,360
- I brought snacks.
- You really know me.

416
00:32:27,440 --> 00:32:28,600
- Hey.
- Yeah!

417
00:32:34,800 --> 00:32:37,720
<i>We're all working so hard these days.</i>

418
00:32:37,800 --> 00:32:40,560
<i>And I'm not giving up either.</i>

419
00:32:40,640 --> 00:32:42,360
<i>To get here,</i>

420
00:32:42,440 --> 00:32:44,360
<i>I've cried so many tears.</i>

421
00:32:46,560 --> 00:32:50,040
<i>From now on,</i>
<i>I'll live my life to the fullest,</i>

422
00:32:50,560 --> 00:32:53,200
<i>for Mom, for myself,</i>

423
00:32:53,280 --> 00:32:55,280
<i>and for the people I love.</i>

424
00:32:57,160 --> 00:32:58,200
How is it?

425
00:33:04,680 --> 00:33:05,720
Did you get in?

426
00:33:07,000 --> 00:33:08,680
Chula Med School, Mom!

427
00:33:10,080 --> 00:33:12,480
Oh my god, my baby. You're the best!

428
00:33:12,560 --> 00:33:14,040
You're amazing.

429
00:33:14,120 --> 00:33:15,160
You're the best.

430
00:33:16,200 --> 00:33:17,200
Here.

431
00:33:17,280 --> 00:33:18,600
I have to record this.

432
00:33:18,680 --> 00:33:19,640
Wow.

433
00:33:34,960 --> 00:33:35,800
Mom,

434
00:33:36,840 --> 00:33:38,640
I got into Chula Med School.

435
00:33:39,600 --> 00:33:41,640
<i>Oh, I'm so happy for you, son.</i>

436
00:33:41,720 --> 00:33:45,040
<i>You're incredible. I'm so proud of you.</i>

437
00:33:47,360 --> 00:33:48,360
I love you, Mom.

438
00:33:49,760 --> 00:33:51,000
Please tell Dad I love him too.

439
00:33:51,080 --> 00:33:53,560
<i>Of course, sweetheart.</i>

440
00:33:53,640 --> 00:33:56,400
<i>But why tell me all of a sudden?</i>

441
00:33:56,480 --> 00:33:58,600
Because I do love you.
I just wanted to say it.

442
00:33:59,600 --> 00:34:00,800
That's all.

443
00:34:08,840 --> 00:34:10,639
- Mom.
- Hm?

444
00:34:11,159 --> 00:34:13,600
I'll study hard.

445
00:34:14,120 --> 00:34:16,040
I'll do my very best.

446
00:34:18,040 --> 00:34:20,159
And I'll be a good mom,

447
00:34:20,239 --> 00:34:22,560
under my good daughter's guidance.

448
00:34:22,639 --> 00:34:25,639
Mom, that's a bit over the top.

449
00:34:27,080 --> 00:34:29,239
Sweetheart, do whatever you want to do.

450
00:34:29,960 --> 00:34:33,199
If you want to play music,
or do anything else,

451
00:34:33,719 --> 00:34:35,199
you can do anything

452
00:34:35,920 --> 00:34:37,360
that makes you happy.

453
00:34:38,120 --> 00:34:39,560
Thank you.

454
00:34:40,600 --> 00:34:42,600
Come on, let's sleep.

455
00:34:43,239 --> 00:34:45,320
- Good night.
- Good night, dear.

456
00:34:49,880 --> 00:34:52,280
Okay, now

457
00:34:52,360 --> 00:34:55,719
let me tell you
the schedule first, everyone.

458
00:34:56,480 --> 00:34:57,880
- Say it.
- So,

459
00:34:58,400 --> 00:35:01,040
we're starting our tour soon.

460
00:35:01,640 --> 00:35:03,240
- Damn.
- Alright?

461
00:35:03,320 --> 00:35:05,760
- A tour?
- And, it'll start next month.

462
00:35:05,840 --> 00:35:08,480
We'll begin with a school tour,

463
00:35:08,560 --> 00:35:09,920
- going around different schools.
- Mm.

464
00:35:10,000 --> 00:35:16,040
It'll take about two days a week,

465
00:35:16,640 --> 00:35:19,520
so I wanted to ask Nana
if you can take leave from school.

466
00:35:21,120 --> 00:35:22,480
I'm not sure.

467
00:35:23,000 --> 00:35:27,040
I just went back to high school,
I'm still adjusting.

468
00:35:27,120 --> 00:35:30,080
All my friends my age
are already in college.

469
00:35:31,320 --> 00:35:33,440
Come on, hang in there.

470
00:35:33,520 --> 00:35:36,520
You don't get your school days back
once they're gone.

471
00:35:37,200 --> 00:35:38,040
Yeah, but…

472
00:35:38,680 --> 00:35:40,360
just take leave. Or drop out.

473
00:35:40,440 --> 00:35:42,120
- Hey.
- No.

474
00:35:42,800 --> 00:35:43,840
Whoa.

475
00:35:43,920 --> 00:35:46,360
- Just kidding.
- Then talk to your teacher first.

476
00:35:46,440 --> 00:35:48,320
See if you can take a break.

477
00:35:48,400 --> 00:35:51,920
If not, we'll figure out the schedule.

478
00:35:52,000 --> 00:35:53,240
- Yeah, yeah.
- Mm.

479
00:35:53,760 --> 00:35:57,560
- Oh yeah, one more thing.
- What?

480
00:35:58,640 --> 00:36:02,160
From today on, I'd like

481
00:36:04,240 --> 00:36:06,480
to appoint Alice as the new band leader.

482
00:36:06,560 --> 00:36:07,480
- Hm?
- Huh?

483
00:36:08,000 --> 00:36:09,200
Are you serious?

484
00:36:09,280 --> 00:36:10,360
For real?

485
00:36:10,440 --> 00:36:12,880
You can't. Why?

486
00:36:13,480 --> 00:36:16,640
Well, you have great leadership skills.

487
00:36:17,160 --> 00:36:20,160
You also wrote the band's first song,

488
00:36:20,240 --> 00:36:22,760
and it became a big hit.

489
00:36:23,600 --> 00:36:27,240
So, I'm officially handing
the title of Rock & Soul's leader

490
00:36:27,320 --> 00:36:29,560
to you.

491
00:36:29,640 --> 00:36:30,640
- Uh--
- Hey.

492
00:36:31,240 --> 00:36:32,920
- No objections, everyone.
- Huh?

493
00:36:34,640 --> 00:36:38,800
Fine, but only for one year.

494
00:36:38,880 --> 00:36:40,880
Next year, you have to take it back.

495
00:36:40,960 --> 00:36:44,200
Uh, can I lead us next year? Please?

496
00:36:44,280 --> 00:36:45,240
Please, I volunteer.

497
00:36:45,320 --> 00:36:46,720
- You'll crash the band.
- Yeah.

498
00:36:46,800 --> 00:36:48,640
