499
00:36:50,280 --> 00:36:51,280
I…

500
00:36:52,720 --> 00:36:54,240
I can't promise.

501
00:36:54,320 --> 00:36:56,600
Let's see how it goes first.

502
00:36:57,840 --> 00:36:58,800
Let's continue.

503
00:36:58,880 --> 00:37:00,040
- Alright.
- Okay.

504
00:37:00,120 --> 00:37:02,640
